Package: rmetrics
Type: Package
Title: A Collection of Metrics to Evaluate the Performance of Statistical and Machine Learning Models
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonas", "Schropp", , "jonas.schropp@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The package provides a common interface to a very large collection of metrics for the evaluation of machine learning models and statistical models. 
    It is mainly designed as a backend for the revaluate package, but each function can of course be used on its own.
